    • RemoteExtensionActionRequest

      public RemoteExtensionActionRequest(String action, String requestClass, byte[] requestBytes)
      RemoteExtensionActionRequest constructor with class names and request bytes. Does not require a dependency on the remote extension code.
      Parameters:
      action - A string representing the fully qualified class name of the remote ActionType instance
      requestClass - A string representing the fully qualified class name of the remote ActionRequest class
      requestBytes - Bytes representing the serialized parameters to be used in the ActionRequest class StreamInput constructor
